{"tid":716733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上個世紀60、70年代的伊朗，一個開放繁榮的西方化國家","createTime":"2018-06-25T13:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T13:41:31.000Z","uid":49071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7e304c284dbd9d453cdbfde7368851e104675849","tid":716733,"uid":49071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:40:45.000Z","msg":"成日睇新聞都覺得伊朗係一個好保守好封閉既地方,原來以前幾開放幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從19世紀下半葉到20世紀初，隨着歐洲列強的侵入，伊朗逐漸淪為半殖民地國家，社會經濟衰落，封建統治專橫殘暴。<br />\n1921年，軍官利薩汗發動政變，奪取了政權，建立了巴列維王朝。在其執政期間，美國為了獲得伊朗的石油及保持在伊朗的利益，大力扶持巴列維王朝。<br />\n<br />\n現在提起伊朗你首先會想到什麼呢？女人無地位，跟美國對抗，刻板的宗教規矩&hellip;&hellip;等等，總之給人的感覺是伊朗是一個不太開 放，比較保守的國家。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=2f7101a/509o0000596q764o9883.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2f7101a%2F509o0000596q764o9883.jpg&h=1a0674ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=t95bh3/1821/6692229742.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dt95bh3%2F1821%2F6692229742.jpg&h=f0350883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然而上世紀60、70年代的伊朗可不是這樣的，當時正是巴列維王朝時期（1925年&mdash;1979年），他們的國王穆罕默德&middot;巴列維推行 親英美的政策，社會生活方面也趨於英美化，那時候的伊朗簡直就是一個標準的西方國家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=3v5lrdh/50990000q5r40734n87o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3v5lrdh%2F50990000q5r40734n87o.jpg&h=f818368e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=nvcr5v/50990000q5r68s52s310.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dnvcr5v%2F50990000q5r68s52s310.jpg&h=93ab4818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=2b7qb8r/509p00005q61qns395o1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2b7qb8r%2F509p00005q61qns395o1.jpg&h=9dfdf2cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=30tfcvh/1820/6656249323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D30tfcvh%2F1820%2F6656249323.jpg&h=7c527aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=3vskg71/50980000rn8251677938.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3vskg71%2F50980000rn8251677938.jpg&h=d5ff1aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=2al6t91/509n0000o4o882qo2872.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2al6t91%2F509n0000o4o882qo2872.jpg&h=4f9004b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=1n8j075/5096000435rs52n8pq1q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1n8j075%2F5096000435rs52n8pq1q.jpg&h=c5ca50f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"042a9590c702aaa0616efdee1b85b819f5eaca7f","tid":716733,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:41:31.000Z","msg":"hello moto"}]}